race.description: Bet Nation North Queensland Cup H
race.comment: JACKKNIFED (5) was rewarded for his honesty after three minors on end with a deserved win last time, scoring at this track over 380m (21.95). Goes very well from this draw with three wins and three minor placings from six starts. One of the key runners again. HARA'S OSCAR (1) found trouble in the run at this course and distance last time and fell. Expected to feature on best. BARNSLEY (6) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 5 last run (29.29) at this track. Can feature again. FLAMING COMET (2) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.
